tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE network_coverage_analysis (
  location_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  location_name VARCHAR(255),
  longitude DECIMAL(10, 8),
  latitude DECIMAL(10, 8),
  network_strength INT
);

CREATE TABLE coverage_zones (
    zone_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    min_latitude FLOAT,
    max_latitude FLOAT,
    min_longitude FLOAT,
    max_longitude FLOAT,
    network_type VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE LocationData (
    location_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    latitude FLOAT,
    longitude FLOAT,
    network_provider VARCHAR,
    signal_strength INT
);

CREATE TABLE CoverageAreas (
    area_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    covered_location_id INT,
    coverage_range FLOAT,
    network_provider VARCHAR,
    population_density INT
);

CREATE TABLE OptimizedCoverage (
    optimized_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    provider_id INT,
    optimized_area_id INT,
    data_speed INT,
    signal_quality VARCHAR
);

CREATE TABLE UserFeedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    provider_id INT,
    feedback_text VARCHAR,
    rating INT
);
